idth=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ignatia>Ignatia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(8/1/01 8:42:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Character sheet...please reply!</span><hr size=1> i shoulda explained something...Ignatia was originally in this group that defended the world (it's not really earth, considering it's a whole different solar system similar to ours, but not quite, considering that people can live on more then one planet) with Ajina and Trinn. The whole bit about the weapons is the weapons that she used while in the group. Then, she and the other two formed a Manga group called &quot;Paranoia&quot; with Kokoro and Opal (Paranoia does actually exist, me and my friends are the main characters in this). And the tiger claws are a set of gloves with hooks at the knuckle.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ugothicchaos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gothic chaos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(8/1/01 9:20:50 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Character sheet...please reply!</span><hr size=1> yeah,i know what tiger claws are,i just don't care for them.(i prefer projectile weapons because if i miss i cna run away because i'm a little wuss <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) Okay,now,about this defending the world thing,perhaps go into a bit more detail. Like,did they fail and thats why she's here?Or after things were over something caused her to come to the place she is now. Another thing,i'm guessing this character is based off yourself. While 